# {{context|uncountable|lang=en}} The natural medium emanating from the Sun and other very hot sources (now recognised as electromagnetic radiation with a wavelength of 400-750 nm), within which vision is possible.
#: {{usex|lang=en|As you can see, this spacious dining-room gets a lot of '''light''' in the mornings.}}
